            <h2 class="dp-section-title">Self-Taught. Battle-Tested. 28 Years Deep.</h2>
            <p class="dp-section-desc">
              Learned to type on a typewriter. Learned to code hacking computer labs. Bought books off Amazon
              before Amazon sold anything else. Spoke at DrupalCons around the world. Created the #3 theme in all of Drupal.
              Contracted 7 years before they finally said yes. Published author. Principal Engineer. Startup founder.
              This is the trajectory.
            </p>
