              <div class="dp-timeline-content">
                <div class="dp-timeline-title">Amazon.com Was Still a Bookstore</div>
                <div class="dp-timeline-desc">Ordered every programming book Amazon carried -- back when that's all they sold. CSS, PHP, JavaScript, server administration. Earned mastery the hard way: reading covers to covers, building things that broke until they didn't, and doing it all over again on a dial-up connection in the mountains of Colorado.</div>
